380
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:45,599
Aku akan segera menikahinya.

381
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:49,309
Jadi, jangan muncul lagi atau mencariku.

382
00:17:49,309 --> 00:17:50,839
Aku bahkan tidak mau melihatmu.

383
00:17:50,970 --> 00:17:52,180
Paham?

384
00:17:55,379 --> 00:17:57,550
Apa? Kalian akan menikah?

385
00:17:58,349 --> 00:18:01,250
- Sudah ada orang lain?
- Ya.

386
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,119
Jadi, pergilah!

387
00:18:12,530 --> 00:18:13,629
Hong Joo.

388
00:18:14,260 --> 00:18:15,430
Kamu baik-baik saja?

389
00:18:15,669 --> 00:18:18,030
- Ya, Pak Kang.
- Jadi,

390
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:20,099
