00:19:07,619 --> 00:19:09,389
Kukira itu cinta.

402
00:19:11,220 --> 00:19:13,819
Aku bahkan membayarinya berkuliah di Amerika.

403
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:17,359
Tapi dia mengkhianatiku

404
00:19:17,829 --> 00:19:20,000
