411
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:45,119
hidupku akan sia-sia.

412
00:19:47,159 --> 00:19:48,319
Tapi

413
00:19:49,159 --> 00:19:52,730
aku bersyukur karena dia membantuku bertemu dengan Freddie.

414
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:55,829
