445
00:22:05,129 --> 00:22:07,599
- Tampaknya begitu.
- Itu buruk.

446
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:11,169
Kejutan.

447
00:22:11,169 --> 00:22:12,369
Apa ini?

448
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:16,510
